description:
In what ways does planet Earth differ from other planets?

This #short clip from the Global Campmeeting sermon, “What Makes Earth So Unique and Special? #Campmeeting” https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Mz_jW5UC_Ms&list=PL-k2Gb-DBYo9tb9fHW_AxGxJ1R8MpNnpa&index=32  discusses our planet’s uniqueness in comparison to other planets. Earth is the only place in the universe where there is life and life is sustainable, which alone makes it unique and special.

God didn’t make the world empty; He designed it to be inhabited. He created this world to be a beautiful place for us to live in.

Watch the video to learn more about what makes Earth unique and special.
